		<p class=3D"note"><span class=3D"note-title">Note:</span> Make sure that =
the <span class=3D"cs-variable"><u>M</u>ann-Whitney U</span> checkbox is ti=
cked in the <span class=3D"areas">=E2=80=93Test Type=E2=80=93</span> area a=
